        "body": "We were coming from Khaibar along with Allah's Messenger (ﷺ) while l was riding behind Abu Talha and he was proceeding. While one of the wives of Allah's Messenger (ﷺ) was riding behind Allah's Messenger (ﷺ), suddenly the foot of the camel Slipped and I said, \"The woman!\" and alighted (hurriedly). Allah's Apostle said, \"She is your mother.\" Sol resaddled the she-camel and Allah's Messenger (ﷺ) mounted it. When he approached or saw Madina, he said, \"Ayibun, ta'ibun, 'abidun, li-Rabbina hami-dun.\""
